# REST Client tests for Laravel backend

### GET all siswa
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/siswa
Accept: application/json

###

### POST create siswa
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/siswa
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama": "Budi",
  "umur": 15,
  "no_hp_ortu": "082112345678",
  "paket": "Silver"
}

###

### GET siswa by id
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/siswa/1
Accept: application/json

###

### PUT update siswa by id
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/siswa/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama": "Budi Updated",
  "umur": 16,
  "no_hp_ortu": "082199988776",
  "paket": "Gold"
}

###

### DELETE siswa by id
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/siswa/1
Accept: application/json

